James Paulsen, chief investment 
strategist at Wells Capital Management, recommends buying 
emerging market stocks, and U.S. companies in manufacturing, 
industrials, basic materials, and financials. Paulsen talks with
Bloomberg's Ken Prewitt and  Tom Keene  on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 12:38
 